        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>State and Local Corrections Officer Retirement Fairness Act of 2022</strong></p> <p>This bill extends the exemption from the penalty for early withdrawals from tax-exempt retirement plans currently allowed to federal public safety officers to certain state and local government corrections officers.</p>]]>
        </text>
